sharada
sharada lipi font.
Om Svasti Ekam Siddham.
This font has been made for users to start typing on a laptop easily.
Uses Sharada glyphs in Devanagari character unicode space U0900-097F. Also few ligatures for conjuncts, and variant matras.
Please download Devanagari phonetic keyboard map vidyut from http://www.mywhatever.com/sanskrit/vidyut/
Uses glyphs from Unicode Vedic extensions U1CD0 namely dirgha svarita and jihvamulia/upadhmaniya.
Uses Sharada glyphs in Sharada Unicode character space U11180-U111DF.
Jai Gurudev
